column11: Good survey but next time.%0A1. Make the fonts and the bubbles to check larger they were really small and I had to click 2 to 3 times to get the click in the box.%0A2. Put a percentage meter to let us know how much of the quiz we've completed and there is left to go.  At one point i wasn't sure if the test was in an endless loop.  I"ve been in surveys where there was a glitch and it never ended it was in a loop error.  That's it thanks.
